The crusher is used to crush the three clumps of ore we get from the Purification Chamber, but we also have to have Oxygen, so make that machine first.

The Purification Chamber will take our ore and mix it with Oxygen to give up 3 clumps per block of ore.

By sending those clumps to the crusher will get 3 Dirty Dusts back.
We have to get some kind of basic power to run our machines. One of the easiest is the Steam Dynamo from Thermal Expansion.

Oxygen is easy to make using the Electrolytic Seperator. By feeding water in with power, we seperate the water H2O into Hydrogen and Oxygen.

Â§1Guess what, we can even use the Hydrogen as fuel for the Jetpack, so what a deal!

Congrats, You have all the parts needed to make a Tier 2 ore processing system which will triple you ingots.

But how do you hook all this up, well you ask....

Â§1To make the Oxygen for the Purification Chamber.
Water -> Electric Pump -> Electrolytic Seperator -> Oxygen

Â§2Feed the Oxygen into the Purification Chamber

Â§41 Ore -> Purification Chamber -> Crusher -> Enrichment Chamber -> Energized Smelter
